semsim.model.physical

Class PhysicalModelComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • semsim.SemSimObject
      • semsim.model.SemSimComponent
        • semsim.model.physical.PhysicalModelComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PhysicalDependency, PhysicalEntity, PhysicalProcess, PhysicalProperty, PhysicalPropertyInComposite

    public abstract class PhysicalModelComponent
extends SemSimComponent
implements Annotatable
    Class for working with the physical, as opposed to computational, elements in SemSim models. These include physical entities, processes, dependencies, and their associated properties.
    Author:
    mneal
